00:14:09.228 --> 00:14:09.728
telomeres.

243
00:14:10.788 --> 00:14:12.608
And actually, we compare

244
00:14:13.788 --> 00:14:17.528
the phenotype. So the telomerase knockout with the POT1

245
00:14:17.968 --> 00:14:20.008
mutant that we are studying here,

