00:33:14.274 --> 00:33:15.694
mutations in a residue that

571
00:33:15.714 --> 00:33:19.374
this was related by many

572
00:33:19.394 --> 00:33:23.014
different kinases are having such strong phenotypes in mind.

573
00:33:23.094 --> 00:33:26.294
So pointing to the importance of telomere regulation by

574
00:33:26.934 --> 00:33:29.654
extracellular factors,

575
00:33:30.494 --> 00:33:31.534
which is something that we don't

